wikipedia_page.main: Walter Scott Buchanan (1 June 1855 – 11 November 1926) was an English international footballer, who played as a forward.

response: * 1 June – Walter Buchanan (d. 1926), England international in 1876 (one match); played for Clapham Rovers.
